---
title: Butter Shrimp Curry with Basmati and Garlic Flatbread
description: Buttery tikka-flavoured shrimp with garlic flatbread and rice is comfort food with an Indian twist. The best part? The whole meal is ready in as long as it takes to cook the rice.

